Description-Content-Type: text/markdown
License-File: LICENSE

This package provides generic [`chaostoolkit`](https://chaostoolkit.org) modules to simulate *compute* and *network* outages for various cloud providers as well as *pod disruptions* in any Kubernetes cluster.

<img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/gardener/gardener/master/logo/gardener.svg" width="16"/> [Gardener](https://github.com/gardener/gardener) users benefit from an additional module that leverages the generic modules, but simplifies the configuration (no need to specify cloud provider credentials, cluster credentials, or filters explicitly) and makes it also more secure (retrieves credentials and stores them only in memory).

Please check out the original repo [README](https://github.com/gardener/chaos-engineering/blob/main/readme.md) for more information.
